'''Saliou Lassissi''' (born [[15 August]], [[1978]] in [[Abidjan]]) is a [[Côte d'Ivoire]] [[Football (soccer)|football]] player. He is currently plays for [[L'Entente SSG]], after having left [[AC Bellinzona]] on September 2007.<ref>{{cite web|language=Italian|url=http://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/index.php?action=read&id=74549|publisher=TuttoMercatoWeb|title=UFFICIALE: Bellinzona, arrivano Grabbi e Da Mota; Lassissi rescinde|date=[[2007-09-08]]|accessdate=2007-09-08}}</ref>

He also holds French passport.

